Output tui-tour.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.3

Type "veles" Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "/status" Enter
Sleep 2.5s
Type "/context" Enter
Sleep 2.5s
Type "/mode planning" Enter
Sleep 2.5s
Type "/help" Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+D
Sleep 1s
